{"tid":698383,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"正式宣布邊個支持美斯就係支那狗","createTime":"2018-06-11T15:32:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-12T01:04:32.000Z","uid":76310,"like":25,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"73408889fc1ea5a00a0f4d6616ef35bf2f7b93c3","tid":698383,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T15:32:35.000Z","msg":"正式宣布邊個支持美斯就係支那狗<br />\n<br />\n好耐之前已經幫wechat賣廣告<br />\n而家代言埋蒙牛"},{"pid":"d5d14f85ee19b2403857454413e86426d137b85c","tid":698383,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T15:33:26.000Z","msg":"蒙牛=三聚青銨<br />\n幫蒙牛代言, 你地幫小花迷, 記撚住飲多些三聚青銨"},{"pid":"9ceb694ce29a2ac1806a802bdf54abbbdf8ff3bb","tid":698383,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T15:34:31.000Z","msg":"蒙牛邀美斯任品牌代言人　代言費估計每年最少4000萬人幣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1234355/org/86e1b4f6685be8cd92ca47c829d4e6e1.jpg/mHWH9EUbSMuOhuf7uNNxGIzRifDbXNVPHRX36R0V9-k?v=w1600r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1234355%2Forg%2F86e1b4f6685be8cd92ca47c829d4e6e1.jpg%2FmHWH9EUbSMuOhuf7uNNxGIzRifDbXNVPHRX36R0V9-k%3Fv%3Dw1600r16_9&h=e30416ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蒙牛（2319）公布，繼成為2018年FIFA世界盃全球官方贊助商後，又請來阿根廷球星美斯擔任集團品牌代言人。蒙牛認為此舉可助蒙牛引領中國乳業品牌走向世界，逐步建立品牌影響力。"},{"pid":"96d0110e9ec529084052403cb7ac6aecad84ed53","tid":698383,"uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T15:34:57.000Z","msg":"里昂發表研究報告指，蒙牛委任阿根廷球星美斯為代言人後，該行相信短期可強化品牌重建工程，亦標誌其長期全球化野心。該行估算，美斯的代言費大約每年4,000萬至5,000萬元人民幣，相當於蒙牛年度營銷費用約1%。該行認為其新產品料可加快銷售增長，並改善盈利表現。"},{"pid":"2a29dd490b46e0d5bc8592e61a189762c1dbbd34","tid":698383,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T15:35:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1234873/org/5f9d9316b646c80c42c23c7569cd0b39.jpg/j37Srf2Qhd2C3sBvONRKdzs5LVQhqW9Z4XoFQuF6BUI?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.k